fields.value: We've put together comprehensive instructions on how to prepare 3D files in our [doc hub](https://www.notion.so/palatial/b0e713aac77a491c81672fb578cbd896?v=1356c4b15eed4026a9177d72886a4976), and using the web stream is no harder than navigating around Google Maps.
